（雖然最後都玩埋大逆轉2而且覺得ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"3853827aa0a1c17dea14e0c3521a44fa624e58a2","tid":377891,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第四集成日畀人忽視<br />\n成步堂落咗位就屌屌屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最大問題係牙琉個動機太低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb4c62bb04f7f21fe9f440a41a88941997e788e","tid":377891,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bb0c07d264ca60b4be957a1ca94a365a3bf1cd","tid":377891,"uid":110309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"估唔到香港有人討論逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為已經無哂同好,得我自己一個隻隻都買黎玩"},{"pid":"c88b8e492c006aaad1482d457f7888faba79c696","tid":377891,"uid":110309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"大逆必須要1+2咁玩先完整<br />\n大逆1個尾收到差d想講粗口,但連埋大逆2就無問題<br />\n<br />\n逆5個人差,但我反而覺得心音個part描寫得幾好,算係幾話串埋一齊有呼應<br />\n<br />\n逆6感覺好過逆5,而且有レイファ女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真宵又返黎<br />\n故事都算係連貫,最後boss係有d易估但唔影響遊戲,<br />\n因為逆6重點係辯護士身份,唔係對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f9a0914fff65bbdc7bc0993812f81b5161aca5","tid":377891,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到香港有人討論逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為已經無哂同好,得我自己一個隻隻都買黎玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實香港都好多人玩<br />\n上幾個蘋果fb報導美國有單兇殺案<br />\n現場有隻鸚鵡有記低死者嘅說話<br />\n勁多comment講小百合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\